originalText.text: This provider seemingly works with a handful of long-term care providers who pay her to send clients for long-term care their way, with total disregard for the wellbeing and needs of the client. It is a criminal and negligent practice that is inhumane towards the patient and simply aims to stuff the pockets of this provider. She doesn't care, nor does she have the training or heart to care. I would avoid at all costs, there are many wonderful providers in this city! She is the worst mistake I ever made.
